platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Il ny a pas un jour ennuyeux

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Created using gaming industry tech like 3D modeling and lighting effects, (Not Boring) Weather makes local forecasts delightfully interactive. Fun flourishes such as high-fidelity sound effects, charming animations, and just-noticeable haptic feedback make the weather report anything but boring.
